Preheat the George Forman Grilling Machine for 5 minutes. Stir together barbecue sauce, orange peel, ginger in small bowl. Place chicken breasts on Grilling Machine, brushing with one-half sauce; close lid. Cook 4 minutes. Turn chicken over and brush with sauce; close lid. Cook 2 more minutes; add pineapple slices to grill brush with remaining sauce. Cook 2 more minutes or until chicken is no longer pink in center and slices are lightly browned. Serve each chicken with 2-1/2 pineapple slices. Serve with broccoli florets and rice, if desired.